{"id": "6038", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6038", "title": "Eagle Shield", "text": "The Eagle Shield is a &lt;a href=\"greatshield\"&gt;greatshield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Eagle Shield is found on a buttress close to the upper area &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Blighttown\"&gt;Blighttown&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nBoth the lightest and least &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;-reliant greatshield in the game. An extremely versatile shield, it combines heavy deflection, and very high &lt;a href=\"stability\"&gt;stability&lt;/a&gt;, with low stat requirements and &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt; that makes it usable even by non-Strength focused characters. This shield has a standard bash attack and the &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;crystal&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt; is 30.\nResistance defense.\nAlong with &lt;a href=\"Physical\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Elemental\"&gt;Elemental&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction, weapons also have hidden stats that reduce the amount of &lt;a href=\"status\"&gt;status&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt; while blocking. It also has the second best resistance to Curse build-up among &lt;a href=\"greatshields\"&gt;greatshields&lt;/a&gt;.\nNotes.\nPre-&lt;a href=\"patch\"&gt;patch&lt;/a&gt; 1.06, the Eagle shield had 100% &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction."}
