{"id": "4216", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4216", "title": "East-West Shield", "text": "The East-West Shield is a &lt;a href=\"medium%20shield\"&gt;medium shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe East-West Shield is the &lt;a href=\"Starting%20Gifts\"&gt;starting&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"shield\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=\"Cleric\"&gt;Cleric&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"class\"&gt;class&lt;/a&gt;. It can also be purchased from the &lt;a href=\"Undead%20Male%20Merchant\"&gt;Undead Male Merchant&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Undead%20Burg\"&gt;Undead Burg&lt;/a&gt; for 400 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe East-West Shield is ultimately not viable after the very beginning of the game, and is the worst medium shield for blocking &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; attacks, with paltry &lt;a href=\"stability\"&gt;stability&lt;/a&gt; and damage reduction. Even amongst wooden shields, the &lt;a href=\"Wooden%20Shield\"&gt;Wooden Shield&lt;/a&gt; is significantly better. The East-West Shield has medium deflection and fast &lt;a href=\"parry\"&gt;parry&lt;/a&gt; speed. When &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Modification\"&gt;upgraded&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;Crystal&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt; is 16. \nResistance Defense.\nAlong with Physical and &lt;a href=\"Elemental\"&gt;Elemental&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction, weapons also have hidden stats that reduce the amount of &lt;a href=\"status\"&gt;status&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt; while blocking."}
