{"id": "135185", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135185", "title": "Eastern Set (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Eastern Armor Set is a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;medium armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nPurchased from the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20Handmaid\"&gt;Shrine Handmaid&lt;/a&gt; for a total of 23,000 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; after giving her the &lt;a href=\"Easterner%27s%20Ashes\"&gt;Easterner's Ashes&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Eastern Set provides very strong defenses for its weight. While its elemental absorption is mediocre for the most part (it is exceptionally resistant to &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; damage), it provides extremely strong protection against &lt;a href=\"Slash%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; damage and is very resistant to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; buildup, making it especially effective when combatting foes wielding &lt;a href=\"Katanas%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;katanas&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Curved%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;curved swords&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Curved%20Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;curved greatswords&lt;/a&gt;. It also provides a moderate amount of &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt; for its weight."}
