{"id": "134841", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=134841", "title": "Elkhorn Round Shield", "text": "The Elkhorn Round Shield is a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Small Shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nLike other Small Shields, the Elkhorn Round Shield is lacking in defensive capability, boasting relatively poor absorption percentages and low stability. However, it makes up for this with faster &lt;a href=\"Parry%20and%20Riposte%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;parry&lt;/a&gt; frames. Like other wood-based shields, it has higher absorption against &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; damage than can usually be found on shields.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with standard ."}
