{"id": "52369", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52369", "title": "Great Magic Barrier (Dark Souls II)", "text": "Great Magic Barrier is a &lt;a href=\"Miracles%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;miracle&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nWhen cast, Great Magic Barrier covers the caster in a white aura, giving them a boost of 250 to all &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; resistances.\nThe duration of the miracle depends on the caster's &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; and ranges from 18 seconds when the spell is spice down to 10 Faith all the way up to 90 seconds at 42 Faith where the duration scaling caps. \nAlthough Great Magic Barrier provides more raw defense than &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Barrier%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Magic Barrier&lt;/a&gt;, it does not affect allies. This means the lesser version may provide more total damage reduction when playing with friendly &lt;a href=\"Phantom%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;phantoms&lt;/a&gt;.\nAttunement Milestones.\nLike most other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:\nDuration Scaling Information.\nDuration values are listed in seconds. Base duration of this spell only depends on Faith. Base duration shown as well as values with the &lt;a href=\"Lingering%20Dragoncrest%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Lingering Dragoncrest&lt;/a&gt; variants applied and pieces of &lt;a href=\"Northwarder%20Set\"&gt;Northwarder Set&lt;/a&gt; applied. "}
