{"id": "8196", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8196", "title": "Guardian Set", "text": "The Guardian Set is a &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;heavy armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". It is only available in the &lt;a href=\"Artorias%20of%20the%20Abyss\"&gt;Artorias of the Abyss&lt;/a&gt; DLC.\nAvailability.\nThe pieces of this set are found on corpses scattered around the &lt;a href=\"Royal%20Wood\"&gt;Royal Wood&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nWorn by the &lt;a href=\"Guardian\"&gt;Guardian&lt;/a&gt;s of the &lt;a href=\"Royal%20Wood\"&gt;Royal Wood&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Guardian Set cannot be reinforced, however, its base stats are already high enough, and can be ideal for players who favour heavy armor sets but can't afford to upgrade or buy some of the stronger sets (such as the &lt;a href=\"Giant%20Set\"&gt;Giant Set&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Smough%27s%20Set\"&gt;Smough's Set&lt;/a&gt;). It's very effective against &lt;a href=\"slash\"&gt;slash&lt;/a&gt; type attacks, but it's notably weaker against &lt;a href=\"strike\"&gt;strike&lt;/a&gt; type attacks."}
