{"id": "130976", "revid": "1188343", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130976", "title": "Gundyr's Halberd", "text": "Gundyr's Halberd is a &lt;a href=\"Boss%20Soul%20Items%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;soul-transposed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Halberds%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;halberd&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nObtained by transposing the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Champion%20Gundyr\"&gt;Soul of Champion Gundyr&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Ludleth%20of%20Courland\"&gt;Ludleth of Courland&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nAs a halberd utilizing the &lt;a href=\"glaive\"&gt;glaive&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Moveset%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;moveset&lt;/a&gt;, Gundyr's Halberd is able to pull off attacks that has excellent coverage and reach while having the benefit of &lt;a href=\"hyper%20armor\"&gt;hyper armor&lt;/a&gt; on its side. As a soul-transposed weapon, it cannot be buffed nor &lt;a href=\"Infusion%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;infused&lt;/a&gt;, making it unsuitable for a myriad of builds.\nIts &lt;a href=\"weapon%20art\"&gt;weapon art&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Champion%27s%20Charge\"&gt;Champion's Charge&lt;/a&gt;, is a unique version of the &lt;a href=\"Charge\"&gt;Charge&lt;/a&gt; that most other halberds and uniquely, the &lt;a href=\"Astora%20Greatsword\"&gt;Astora Greatsword&lt;/a&gt;, uses. Instead of using a strong attack to extend the charges' length, it transitions into sweeping strong attack that deals high damage."}
