{"id": "45600", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=45600", "title": "Hand Axe (Dark Souls II)", "text": "The Hand Axe is an &lt;a href=\"Axes%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;axe&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA surprisingly strong weapon owing to its decent damage, quick attack speed, and low stamina consumption, and it becomes even stronger if enhanced with a weapon buff like &lt;a href=\"Flame%20Weapon\"&gt;Flame Weapon&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Pine%20Resin\"&gt;Dark Pine Resin&lt;/a&gt;. \nIts main weaknesses is its short range and mediocre durability. "}
{"id": "130267", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130267", "title": "Hand Axe (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Hand Axe is an &lt;a href=\"Axes%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;axe&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA rather unremarkable axe, the Hand Axe has the lowest base damage of any axe weapon with the exception of the &lt;a href=\"Thrall%20Axe\"&gt;Thrall Axe&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Butcher%20Knife%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Butcher Knife&lt;/a&gt; (though the latter will outscale a &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Gem\"&gt;Heavy&lt;/a&gt; Hand Axe at high levels of &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;). It is a very lightweight axe with low stat requirements.\nIts quick speed and unexpected reach for its size does give it the niche of serving as an off-hand weapon for slow, heavy weapons such as &lt;a href=\"Ultra%20Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Ultra Greatswords&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curved%20Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curved Greatswords&lt;/a&gt;. \nUpgrades.\nReinforced with &lt;a href=\"Titanite%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Titanite&lt;/a&gt;."}
