{"id": "150163", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=150163", "title": "Harald Legion Set", "text": "The Harald Legion Set is a &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;heavy armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Harald%20Legion%20Knight\"&gt;Harald Legion Knight&lt;/a&gt;s.\nCharacteristics.\nAlthough comprised of three armor pieces instead of four, the Harald Legion Set provides respectable well-balanced defenses for its weight.\nIts physical defenses are about in line with other sets in its weight class. Its weakness to &lt;a href=\"Strike%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; damage is not far out of line with the rest of its defenses, and the same applies to its resistance to &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage. It also resists &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;status effects&lt;/a&gt; in equal amounts all-around, though because of this its tolerance to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; buildup is lower than what can be found in other plate metal sets. It is also backed by a good &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;poise&lt;/a&gt;-to-weight ratio which allows it to effectively trade against smaller weapons but gives it trouble against larger weapons due to its lower weight."}
