{"id": "7314", "revid": "26269363", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7314", "title": "Hard Leather Set", "text": "The Hard Leather Set is a &lt;a href=\"starting%20armor%20set\"&gt;starting armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe Hard Leather Set is heavier than most &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor sets&lt;/a&gt;; in exchange, it boasts higher damage resistances in general. The Hard Leather Set is unique for having a single piece of armor (the &lt;a href=\"Standard%20Helm\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;) providing &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;; the rest of the set does not provide poise. Despite this higher defense and superb helmet, the &lt;a href=\"Wanderer%20Set\"&gt;Wanderer Set&lt;/a&gt; is a superior in very nearly all regards, with the same &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; defense, it has better &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;poison&lt;/a&gt; resistance, a lower &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt; rating and far better &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; resistance; this excludes the helmet."}
