{"id": "135194", "revid": "1188343", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135194", "title": "Hard Leather Set (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Hard Leather Set is a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;medium armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA classic returning from the previous two games, the Hard Leather Set provides a decent amount of protection across the board and is quite &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;lightweight&lt;/a&gt;. It is generally resistant to all forms of &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; damage, save for being slightly more effective against &lt;a href=\"Strike%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; damage. Its elemental resistances are somewhat lower, being particularly weak to &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage despite not being a plate armor set.\nIt is especially effective against all forms of status effects, particularly against &lt;a href=\"Frost\"&gt;Frost&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; buildup, and also provides an appreciable amount of &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance. It also only provides a token amount of &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;, making it sub-optimal for wielding hyper-armor weapons.\nThis makes it a well-rounded set overall that will work in most situations."}
