{"id": "50809", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50809", "title": "Havel's Helm (Dark Souls II)", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;\n&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nHavel's Helm is a piece in &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;. It is part of &lt;a href=\"Havel%27s%20Set%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Havel's Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nHavel's Helm is available in the &lt;a href=\"Upper%20Gutter\"&gt;Upper Gutter&lt;/a&gt; after receiving the &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Key\"&gt;Forgotten Key&lt;/a&gt; from the &lt;a href=\"Elite%20Giant\"&gt;Elite Giant&lt;/a&gt;s at the bottom of &lt;a href=\"Black%20Gulch\"&gt;Black Gulch&lt;/a&gt;, hidden away near &lt;a href=\"The%20Rotten\"&gt;The Rotten&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nHavel's Set in general is one of the most protective armors in the game. When fully upgraded, only the &lt;a href=\"Smelter%20Demon%20Helm\"&gt;Smelter Demon Helm&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Gyrm%20Warrior%20Greathelm\"&gt;Gyrm Warrior Greathelm&lt;/a&gt; have better &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpgrades.\nRequires &lt;a href=\"Twinkling%20Titanite%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Twinkling Titanite&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
