{"id": "8269", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8269", "title": "Helm of Artorias", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;\n&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Helm of Artorias is a &lt;a href=\"head%20armor\"&gt;head armor&lt;/a&gt; piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Set%20of%20Artorias\"&gt;Set of Artorias&lt;/a&gt;, and only available in the \"&lt;a href=\"Artorias%20of%20the%20Abyss\"&gt;Artorias of the Abyss&lt;/a&gt;\" DLC.\nCharacteristics.\nOne of the &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;lightest&lt;/a&gt; head armors between the &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;medium armor sets&lt;/a&gt;, however, also has lower defenses compared to most of them, except for its &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Resist\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistances, which are above average, with fire being one of the highest out of the medium armors.\nThe face visible beneath the shroud of the helm when &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"hollow\"&gt;hollow&lt;/a&gt; is not the player's face, but rather a pre-textured part of the helm. It is not affected by any aspect of the character creation, such as face type, skin color, or even sex.\nUpgrades.\nRequires 200 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
