{"id": "7901", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7901", "title": "Silver Knight Helm", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Silver Knight Helm is a &lt;a href=\"head%20armor\"&gt;head armor&lt;/a&gt; piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Silver%20Knight%20Set\"&gt;Silver Knight Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nFound in one of the two chests guarded by two &lt;a href=\"Silver%20Knight\"&gt;Silver Knight&lt;/a&gt;s in the trophy room of &lt;a href=\"Anor%20Londo\"&gt;Anor Londo&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThis helm offers high &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20resist\"&gt;Lightning resist&lt;/a&gt; and a very\u00a0small amount of &lt;a href=\"Curse%20resist\"&gt;Curse resist&lt;/a&gt;. It has better defense against &lt;a href=\"Slash%20Defense\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; attacks than the other types of attacks, and weaker against &lt;a href=\"Strike%20Defense\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; attacks.\nUpgrades.\nRequires 200 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
