{"id": "132802", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=132802", "title": "Silvercat Ring (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Silvercat Ring is a &lt;a href=\"rings%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nObtained as a gift from &lt;a href=\"Sirris%20of%20the%20Sunless%20Realms\"&gt;Sirris&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt; after helping her defeat &lt;a href=\"Creighton%20the%20Wanderer%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Creighton&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley\"&gt;Irithyll of the Boreal Valley&lt;/a&gt;.\nTo perform this task, the player must look for Sirris's summon sign near the first half of the bridge that connects the &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley%23Bonfires\"&gt;Irithyll of the Boreal Valley&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley%23Bonfires\"&gt;Central Irithyll&lt;/a&gt; and answer her call. If successful, the next time they visit &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt;, she will greet and thank them for their help, bestowing the ring as a reward."}
