{"id": "3213", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3213", "title": "Small Leather Shield", "text": "The Small Leather Shield is a &lt;a href=\"small%20shield\"&gt;small shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Small Leather Shield is &lt;a href=\"Starting%20Gifts\"&gt;given&lt;/a&gt; to the &lt;a href=\"Sorcerer\"&gt;Sorcerer&lt;/a&gt; class at the beginning of the game. It can also be purchased from the &lt;a href=\"Undead%20Male%20Merchant\"&gt;Undead Male Merchant&lt;/a&gt; for 600 &lt;a href=\"soul\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;s.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Small Leather Shield has light deflection and a fast &lt;a href=\"parry\"&gt;parry&lt;/a&gt; window. The Small Leather Shield is the &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;lightest&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"shield\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; in the game, along with the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Hand\"&gt;Dark Hand&lt;/a&gt;, however can have a total of 50 &lt;a href=\"Stability\"&gt;Stability&lt;/a&gt; at +15 Standard compared to the Dark Hand's 30 Stability.\u00a0 Its &lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28Upgrade%20Path%29\"&gt;crystal&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt; is 20.\nResistance Defense.\nAlong with &lt;a href=\"Physical\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Elemental\"&gt;Elemental&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction, weapons also have hidden stats that reduce the amount of &lt;a href=\"status\"&gt;status&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt; while blocking."}
