{"id": "131139", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=131139", "title": "Small Leather Shield (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Small Leather Shield is a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Small Shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nWith a low stat requirement and very light weight, the Small Leather Shield can be easily equipped by most any build in the game for almost no consequence. As it is a Small Shield, it provides pitiful defense when used to block attacks, even after upgrades.\nHowever, it is one of three shields in the game (along with the &lt;a href=\"Buckler%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Buckler&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Target%20Shield%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Target Shield&lt;/a&gt;) classified as a Parrying Shield, with active parry frames that begin sooner than those of other Small Shields. This makes it an ideal tool for parrying enemy attacks on reaction, rather than on prediction.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with ."}
