{"id": "135220", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135220", "title": "Sorcerer Set (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Sorcerer Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA cloth set, the Sorcerer Set provides decent &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;s for its &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;, and strong &lt;a href=\"elemental%20defense\"&gt;elemental defense&lt;/a&gt;s across the board. It does not resist &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"buildup\"&gt;buildup&lt;/a&gt; well, but has strong &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance."}
