{"id": "133907", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133907", "title": "Soul Greatsword (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Soul Greatsword is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nForms a soul greatsword after a short delay, then swings it in a wide arc in front of the caster, dealing 2.0 times the &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; of the wielded &lt;a href=\"Catalysts%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;catalyst&lt;/a&gt; as &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; damage to all &lt;a href=\"Enemies%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;enemies&lt;/a&gt; struck.\nNotes.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
