{"id": "73925", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=73925", "title": "Soul Spear Barrage", "text": "Soul Spear Barrage is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral information.\nWhen cast, this sorcery sends dozens of miniature &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Spear%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Soul Spears&lt;/a&gt; forward, doing little damage if only one or two hit, but much more significant damage if multiple spears land on one target.\nAttunement milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:"}
{"id": "133905", "revid": "51254358", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133905", "title": "Soul Stream", "text": "Soul Stream (\u30bd\u30a6\u30eb\u306e\u5954\u6d41) is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound on the corpse of a sitting scholar in a short hallway beyond the &lt;a href=\"Boreal%20Outrider%20Knight\"&gt;Boreal Outrider Knight&lt;/a&gt; that is hidden behind an &lt;a href=\"Illusory%20Wall%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;illusory wall&lt;/a&gt; on the fourth floor of the &lt;a href=\"Grand%20Archives\"&gt;Grand Archives&lt;/a&gt;.\nEffect.\nSoul Stream is notable in that it is the only Sorcery that requires two &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; slots.\nThe caster charges their &lt;a href=\"Catalysts%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;catalyst&lt;/a&gt; with power for a few seconds in preparation for firing the spell; during this time, it is possible to walk slowly to change position and aiming direction. Once charging is complete, a wide beam of powerful soul energy is unleashed, inflicting extreme amounts of &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; damage to any enemies caught within its path.\nFor the duration of the attack, no movement is possible. The stream inflicts 6 instances of damage throughout the attack, as well as &lt;a href=\"stagger\"&gt;stagger&lt;/a&gt; and knockdown on enemies caught within; each damage instance will deal between 0.8 to 1.2 times the &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; of the catalyst as Magic damage, increasing in strength with each successive instance. Combined, all 6 damage instances will deal the most amount of raw damage of any Sorcery in the game.\nThe beam has a relatively long effect range, roughly the same range as a &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Spear%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Soul Spear&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\n&lt;tabber&gt;Official translation=\n&lt;/tabber&gt;\nGallery.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
