{"id": "52340", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52340", "title": "Soul Vortex", "text": "Soul Vortex is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nGeneral information.\nCreates a swirling vortex of &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Arrow%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Soul Arrows&lt;/a&gt; that moves forward, dealing damage to enemies hit by the arrows. It is best used against large &lt;a href=\"Enemies%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;enemies&lt;/a&gt; or crowds. Generally speaking, it is better to not &lt;a href=\"lock%20on\"&gt;lock on&lt;/a&gt; to a target with this spell, as the vortex will dissipate when it reaches its target instead of continuing on.\nAttunement milestones.\nLike all other spells, the amount of casts per slot increases upon reaching certain &lt;a href=\"Attunement%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Attunement&lt;/a&gt; milestones:"}
