{"id": "8257", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8257", "title": "Soul of Artorias", "text": "The Soul of Artorias is a consumable item in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Knight%20Artorias\"&gt;Knight Artorias&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in the \"&lt;a href=\"Artorias%20of%20the%20Abyss\"&gt;Artorias of the Abyss&lt;/a&gt;\" DLC.\nGeneral information.\nThe Soul of Artorias can be ascended with a +10 &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;straight sword&lt;/a&gt; (other than the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Straight%20Sword\"&gt;Broken Straight Sword&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Sword%20Hilt\"&gt;Straight Sword Hilt&lt;/a&gt;), &lt;a href=\"Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;greatsword&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"ultra%20greatsword\"&gt;ultra greatsword&lt;/a&gt; to create the &lt;a href=\"Abyss%20Greatsword\"&gt;Abyss Greatsword&lt;/a&gt;. It can also be given to &lt;a href=\"Lord%27s%20Blade%20Ciaran\"&gt;Lord's Blade Ciaran&lt;/a&gt; in return for the &lt;a href=\"Gold%20Tracer\"&gt;Gold Tracer&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Silver%20Tracer\"&gt;Dark Silver Tracer&lt;/a&gt;, although these weapons can also be obtained by killing her without giving her the Soul of Artorias.\nThe Soul of Artorias may be consumed for 16,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;. Feeding it to &lt;a href=\"Kingseeker%20Frampt\"&gt;Frampt&lt;/a&gt; grants 10,000 souls."}
