{"id": "16454", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16454", "title": "Souls of Lords", "text": "The Souls of Lords are special &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; that were discovered within the &lt;a href=\"First%20Flame\"&gt;First Flame&lt;/a&gt;.\nLore.\nDiscovery and war.\nThe Souls of Lords were discovered by the chosen few that \"came from the dark\". &lt;a href=\"Gwyn%2C%20Lord%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Gwyn, Lord of Sunlight&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gravelord%20Nito\"&gt;Nito, the First of the Dead&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Witch%20of%20Izalith\"&gt;The Witch of Izalith&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Furtive%20Pygmy\"&gt;Furtive Pygmy&lt;/a&gt;.\nGwyn, Nito and The Witch of Izalith used the power procured from the Lord Souls to challenge the &lt;a href=\"Everlasting%20Dragons\"&gt;Everlasting Dragons&lt;/a&gt; for dominion of the world and, with the help of others, were successful in their endeavor.\nCreation of Chaos.\nThe Witch of Izalith attempted to recreate her own First Flame by using her Lord Soul, but this resulted in her own demise and the creation of the &lt;a href=\"Bed%20of%20Chaos\"&gt;Bed of Chaos&lt;/a&gt;, mother of all &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;Demons&lt;/a&gt;, who inherited possession of the Soul.\nBequeathed Souls.\n&lt;a href=\"Bequeathed%20Lord%20Soul%20Shard\"&gt;Bequeathed Lord Soul Shard&lt;/a&gt;s are fragments of, Gwyn's Lord Soul and were awarded as gifts. One was given to &lt;a href=\"Seath%20the%20Scaleless\"&gt;Seath the Scaleless&lt;/a&gt; for betraying his own kind. Another was given to the &lt;a href=\"Four%20Kings\"&gt;Four Kings&lt;/a&gt; when Lord Gwyn recognized their foresight as leaders of &lt;a href=\"New%20Londo%20Ruins\"&gt;New Londo&lt;/a&gt;.\nDark Soul.\nThe fourth Soul that was discovered by the &lt;a href=\"Furtive%20Pygmy\"&gt;Furtive Pygmy&lt;/a&gt;, ancestor to the &lt;a href=\"Chosen%20Undead\"&gt;Chosen Undead&lt;/a&gt;, was a unique Soul, the \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Soul\"&gt;Dark Soul&lt;/a&gt;\". With it, he waited for Fire to subside so that the Dark Lord could one day be born amongst the humans and bring about the &lt;a href=\"Age%20of%20Dark\"&gt;Age of Dark&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nTwo &lt;a href=\"Lord%20Soul\"&gt;Lord Soul&lt;/a&gt;s and both of the &lt;a href=\"Bequeathed%20Lord%20Soul%20Shard\"&gt;Bequeathed Lord Soul Shard&lt;/a&gt;s are required to satiate the &lt;a href=\"Lordvessel\"&gt;Lordvessel&lt;/a&gt;, allowing the &lt;a href=\"Chosen%20Undead\"&gt;Chosen Undead&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0to enter\u00a0the &lt;a href=\"Kiln%20of%20the%20First%20Flame\"&gt;Kiln of the First Flame&lt;/a&gt; so that he or she may confront &lt;a href=\"Gwyn%2C%20Lord%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Gwyn, Lord of Cinder&lt;/a&gt;."}
