{"id": "60104", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=60104", "title": "Memory of Vammar", "text": "The Memory of Vammar is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nThe memory of the &lt;a href=\"Giant%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;giant&lt;/a&gt; that resides in the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Forest%20of%20Fallen%20Giants\"&gt;Forest of Fallen Giants&lt;/a&gt;. The\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Ashen%20Mist%20Heart\"&gt;Ashen Mist Heart&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0from the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Dragon\"&gt;Ancient Dragon&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0is needed to go here. The giant is located to the right where the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Old%20Ironclad%20Soldier\"&gt;Old Ironclad Soldier&lt;/a&gt; guards the pathway to\u00a0&lt;a href=\"The%20Pursuer\"&gt;The Pursuer&lt;/a&gt;, near the flammable barrels.\nBe warned, only a limited time can be spent in the memory, although it can be revisited at any time."}
{"id": "85780", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=85780", "title": "Memory of the King", "text": "The Memory of the King is a &lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nUpon downloading the \"&lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Sunken%20King\"&gt;Crown of the Sunken King&lt;/a&gt;\" DLC and obtaining the &lt;a href=\"Ashen%20Mist%20Heart\"&gt;Ashen Mist Heart&lt;/a&gt;, the player can enter a memory of &lt;a href=\"Vendrick\"&gt;Vendrick&lt;/a&gt; from before he went &lt;a href=\"hollow\"&gt;hollow&lt;/a&gt;. The memory is accessed through the pile of armor in Vendrick's arena, whether or not he has been slain. In the memory, Vendrick will be unhollowed and completely sane, allowing one to speak with him.\nVendrick's blessing.\nIf the player has obtained the &lt;a href=\"King%27s%20Crown\"&gt;King's Crown&lt;/a&gt; along with the rest of the ancient crowns (&lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Sunken%20King%20%28helm%29\"&gt;Crown of the Sunken King&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Old%20Iron%20King%20%28helm%29\"&gt;Old Iron King&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Ivory%20King%20%28helm%29\"&gt;Ivory King&lt;/a&gt;) and bring them to &lt;a href=\"Vendrick\"&gt;Vendrick&lt;/a&gt; in this place, he will grant them his blessing, which infuses them all with a hidden ability that prevents the player from becoming &lt;a href=\"hollow\"&gt;hollow&lt;/a&gt; by any means while wearing any of them and also grants immunity against the &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; status ailment."}
{"id": "91748", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=91748", "title": "Memory of the Old Iron King", "text": "The Memory of the Old Iron King is a &lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nThe Memory of the Old Iron King is located at the top of &lt;a href=\"Brume%20Tower\"&gt;Brume Tower&lt;/a&gt;. It is located within the &lt;a href=\"Alonne%27s%20Set\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Bewitched%20Alonne%20Sword\"&gt;weapon&lt;/a&gt; once used by &lt;a href=\"Sir%20Alonne\"&gt;Sir Alonne&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Ashen%20Mist%20Heart\"&gt;Ashen Mist Heart&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Old%20Iron%20King%20%28helm%29\"&gt;Crown of the Old Iron King&lt;/a&gt; are needed to enter the memory. \nThe player can stay in the Memory of the Old Iron King only for a limited amount of time. After 18 minutes have passed, the memory will end the player will automatically be returned to Brume Tower."}
