{"id": "133983", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=133983", "title": "Mendicant's Staff", "text": "The Mendicant's Staff is a &lt;a href=\"Staves%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;staff&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Man%20Serpent%20Summoner\"&gt;Man Serpent Summoner&lt;/a&gt;s in &lt;a href=\"Archdragon%20Peak\"&gt;Archdragon Peak&lt;/a&gt;\nCharacteristics.\nThe Mendicant's Staff is a poor-performing catalyst, only consistently possessing superior &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; compared to the &lt;a href=\"Witchtree%20Branch%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Witchtree Branch&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Sage%27s%20Crystal%20Staff\"&gt;Sage's Crystal Staff&lt;/a&gt;; even in this situation, the Sage's Crystal Staff can easily surpass it via the use of its skill.\nThe staff's saving grace is that it possesses a &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;soul&lt;/a&gt;-absorbing bonus, much like the &lt;a href=\"Shield%20of%20Want\"&gt;Shield of Want&lt;/a&gt;, in that any enemy that dies while this staff is being wielded will award an additional 20% of its soul bounty. This bonus can be stacked with other tools with soul bounty increasing effects such as the Shield of Want, &lt;a href=\"Covetous%20Silver%20Serpent%20Ring%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Covetous Silver Serpent Ring&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Symbol%20of%20Avarice%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Symbol of Avarice&lt;/a&gt;, and as such, can be a useful tool for farming souls.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with standard ."}
