{"id": "173158", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=173158", "title": "Mercenary", "text": "The Mercenary is one of the &lt;a href=\"Classes%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;classes&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%203\"&gt;Dark Souls 3&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIt is a &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;-based class, with just enough &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; to cast several basic &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Sorceries&lt;/a&gt; such as &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Arrow%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Soul Arrow&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Spook\"&gt;Spook&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Weapon%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic Weapon&lt;/a&gt;, provided a &lt;a href=\"Sorcerer%27s%20Staff%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Sorcerer's Staff&lt;/a&gt; is bought from the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20Handmaid\"&gt;Shrine Handmaid&lt;/a&gt;. \nThe starting weapon, the &lt;a href=\"Sellsword%20Twinblades\"&gt;Sellsword Twinblades&lt;/a&gt;, is one of the strongest weapons in the game and is capable of inflicting extreme damage when two-handed since it is a &lt;a href=\"Paired%20Weapons\"&gt;Paired Weapon&lt;/a&gt; and therefore will attack with both weapons when the block button is pressed. Its Weapon Art, &lt;a href=\"Spin%20Slash%20%28Twinblades%29\"&gt;Spin Slash&lt;/a&gt;, isn't strong in and of itself but has two strong advantages in that it is unparriable and that a light attack or a block/dual attack combos directly into the Spin Slash and its heavy attack follow up, allowing a devastating combo against lightly armored foes. The &lt;a href=\"Wooden%20Shield%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Wooden Shield&lt;/a&gt;, however, has fallen quite far since its glory days in the previous games due to its poor physical blocking and is mostly only useful for parrying. \nThe &lt;a href=\"Sellsword%20Set\"&gt;Sellsword Set&lt;/a&gt; it wears is decent, having good defences for its weight and being fairly light but has mediocre &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;, though since the class is unlikely to be used for a build using a &lt;a href=\"Hyper%20Armor\"&gt;Hyper Armor&lt;/a&gt;-supported weapon (except for maybe the &lt;a href=\"Astora%20Greatsword\"&gt;Astora Greatsword&lt;/a&gt;) this might not be relevant. \nThe &lt;a href=\"Uchigatana%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Uchigatana&lt;/a&gt; is another strong weapon suitable for this class, and is obtainable early on if a slower Dexterity-based weapon is desired. "}
