{"id": "143665", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=143665", "title": "Millwood Knight Set", "text": "The Millwood Knight Set is a &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;heavy armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nAvailability.\nPurchased from the &lt;a href=\"Shrine%20Handmaid\"&gt;Shrine Handmaid&lt;/a&gt; for a total of 23,500 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; after giving her the &lt;a href=\"Captain%27s%20Ashes\"&gt;Captain's Ashes&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nWhile quite hefty, the Millwood Knight Set provides strong all-round defenses that make it an excellent heavy armor set.\nThe set's greatest strengths are its &lt;a href=\"Regular%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Standard&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Slash%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; absorption. While it is weak to &lt;a href=\"Strike%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt;, it is still quite resistant to it, as it is only marginally lower than its &lt;a href=\"Thrust%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Thrust&lt;/a&gt; defense. Its elemental resistances are moderate but sound across the board, with its resistance to &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; matching that of its resistance to &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt;, with the other resistances only negligibly weaker. It also tolerates &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;status effect&lt;/a&gt; buildup very well across the board, save for a weakness to &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt;, which is rarely encountered.\nIt has a high &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;poise&lt;/a&gt;-to-weight ratio to back up its heavy weight, allowing it to even wield &lt;a href=\"Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Greatswords&lt;/a&gt; and trade with similar weapons."}
