{"id": "135206", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135206", "title": "Mirrah Chain Set", "text": "The Mirrah Chain Set is a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;medium armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley\"&gt;Irithyll of the Boreal Valley&lt;/a&gt;. After defeating &lt;a href=\"Creighton%20the%20Wanderer%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Creighton of Mirrah&lt;/a&gt; when he invades in the graveyard past the &lt;a href=\"Church%20of%20Yorshka\"&gt;Church of Yorshka&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt;, return to the bridge that leads into Central Irithyll. The set can be found on a corpse in the middle of the bridge where Creighton was first fought.\nCharacteristics.\n&lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;Weighing&lt;/a&gt; in on the higher end of medium armor sets, the Mirrah Chain Set provides an interesting spread of defenses. Beyond its strong &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; absorption, it is quite resistant to &lt;a href=\"Slash%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; damage and has respectable resistance to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; build-up, making it very strong against &lt;a href=\"Curved%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;curved swords&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Katanas%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;katanas&lt;/a&gt; while maintaining other defenses.\nIts &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; resistances are largely average, though like other metal-based sets it is weak to &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage. It also provides a good amount of &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt; due to its weight."}
