{"id": "135207", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135207", "title": "Mirrah Set", "text": "The Mirrah Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe Mirrah Set offers strong all-round defenses. It is quite strong against &lt;a href=\"Strike\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage, and offers good defense against standard damage as well. It also provides impressive all-round defenses against &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;status effects&lt;/a&gt;. However, its greatest weaknesses are against &lt;a href=\"Slash\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Thrust\"&gt;Thrust&lt;/a&gt; damage, and the set provides little in the way of &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt; despite its moderate &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "61904", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=61904", "title": "Mirrah Shield", "text": "The Mirrah Shield is a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;medium shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in &lt;a href=\"Earthen%20Peak\"&gt;Earthen Peak&lt;/a&gt; in a metal chest at the top of an elevating platform, soon after the &lt;a href=\"Central%20Earthen%20Peak\"&gt;Central Earthen Peak&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nBoasts sub-par elemental defenses, average &lt;a href=\"stability\"&gt;stability&lt;/a&gt;, and overall poor resistances to all &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;negative status effects&lt;/a&gt;. On top of this, it lacks a 100% &lt;a href=\"Physical%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt; damage reduction, making it rather unattractive for its &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;."}
