{"id": "62341", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=62341", "title": "Moon Butterfly Cuffs", "text": "Moon Butterfly Cuffs is a &lt;a href=\"Hands%20Armor%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;hands armor&lt;/a&gt; piece in &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;. It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Moon%20Butterfly%20Set\"&gt;Moon Butterfly Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nCan be purchased from &lt;a href=\"Maughlin%20the%20Armorer\"&gt;Maughlin the Armorer&lt;/a&gt; after spending 16,000 &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; at his shop, for 10,000 souls.\nEffects.\nLike the rest of the set, the Moon Butterfly Cuffs &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;poison&lt;/a&gt; nearby &lt;a href=\"Enemies%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;enemies&lt;/a&gt;, including &lt;a href=\"Characters%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;NPCs&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "53845", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=53845", "title": "Moon Butterfly Hat", "text": "The is a in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Moon%20Butterfly%20Set\"&gt;Moon Butterfly Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nSold by\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Maughlin%20the%20Armorer\"&gt;Maughlin the Armorer&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Majula\"&gt;Majula&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0when the &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20Intensity\"&gt;Intensity&lt;/a&gt; is at least 3 and after spending 16000 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; in his shop. &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20Ascetics\"&gt;Bonfire Ascetics&lt;/a&gt; may be used to acquire this piece."}
